reviewText: It was not what I was looking for in a show. All the stars that I was looking for did not show up for the interview. I want to see all the main stars.
Title: The Closer: Cast & Creators Live at the Paley Center

reviewText: What an fun hour, seeing and hearing these people all as they are in real life! Very interesting anecdotes, and very enjoyable for anyone who loves The Closer!
summary: GREAT to see them out of role
Title: The Closer: Cast & Creators Live at the Paley Center

reviewText: I loved the series and thought that this would be interesting.  It wasn't. Instead it was just a group of ordinary people speaking without benefit of writers.
Title: The Closer: Cast & Creators Live at the Paley Center

reviewText: I have watched many of the interview shows from the Paley Center. The Closer Cast stands out as one of the best. Very professional, done with candor and shows a true understanding of role their audience plays. Highly recommend you watch it. If you love the show, the interview is insight into the characters and actors. Kyra lovers will enjoy her candid views and genuine love for her character.  If you can;t gt enough of The Closer, watch this show.
Title: The Closer: Cast & Creators Live at the Paley Center

reviewText: Where was Lt Provencia? Without him the show would not have lasted this long. He added so much to the show.
Title: The Closer: Cast & Creators Live at the Paley Center
